#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/pgp-expired.page:37
msgid ""
"Depending on how long you want your key to be valid, you can <link xref=\"pgp-"
"create#advanced\">set an expiration date</link> for it. By default, "
"<app>Passwords and Keys</app> sets all keys to be valid forever. That is, the "
